  • Packages that use MetaFields 
    Package Description
    cdm.base.datetime
    Basic date and time concepts: relative date, date range, offset, business centre etc.
    cdm.base.datetime.metafields  
    cdm.base.math
    Basic maths concepts: quantity and unit, rounding, curve / schedule, non-negativity constraint etc.
    cdm.base.math.metafields  
    cdm.base.staticdata.asset.common
    Basic static asset concepts that apply across asset classes: taxonomy etc.
    cdm.base.staticdata.asset.common.metafields  
    cdm.base.staticdata.asset.rates.metafields  
    cdm.base.staticdata.identifier
    Basic identifier and assigned identifier concepts that are applicable across the model.
    cdm.base.staticdata.identifier.metafields  
    cdm.base.staticdata.party
    Basic party concepts: legal entity, natural person, contact details, buyer / payer and all related enums.
    cdm.base.staticdata.party.metafields  
    cdm.event.common
    Business event concepts: primitives, contract state and associated state transition function specifications.
    cdm.event.position
    Position concepts: portfolio and portfolio aggregation.
    cdm.event.workflow
    Workflow concepts (orthogonal to business event): time stamp, credit limit, trade warehouse info and associated function specifications.
    cdm.event.workflow.metafields  
    cdm.legalagreement.common
    Common legal agreement concepts.
    cdm.legalagreement.common.metafields  
    cdm.legalagreement.contract.metafields  
    cdm.legalagreement.csa
    Credit support concepts: CSA, collateral, elections, initial margin, threshold, minimum transfer amount.
    cdm.legalagreement.csa.metafields  
    cdm.legalagreement.master.metafields  
    cdm.observable.asset
    Observable concepts applicable to assets: price, reference price, valuation method etc.
    cdm.observable.asset.metafields  
    cdm.observable.event
    Observable event concepts: extraordinary event, trigger event, disruption event etc.
    cdm.observable.event.metafields  
    cdm.product.asset
    Product concepts applicable to specific asset classes.
    cdm.product.asset.metafields  
    cdm.product.common.schedule
    Common product schedule concepts: calculation period, reset, fixing and payment dates, stub, notional schedule, roll convention.
    cdm.product.common.settlement
    Common product settlement concepts: cash vs physical, non-deliverable, money and cashflow, delivery vs payment.
    cdm.product.template
    Template feature concepts to define payouts.
